    <div class="brutalist-card">
        <h2>Problem It Solves</h2>
        <p>In today's fast-paced digital work environment, professionals are overwhelmed by context switching and scattered communication. Tasks, deadlines, and critical updates are fragmented across emails, chat applications, and manual to-do lists.</p>
        <p>This leads to missed deadlines, increased burnout, and a reactive workflow rather than a proactive one. Niyro solves this by acting as a centralized intelligence layer that automatically aggregates tasks, prioritizes what matters, and actively blocks out distractions so you can execute without burning out.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="brutalist-card">
        <h2>Solution Overview</h2>
        <p>Niyro is an AI-powered, context-aware productivity assistant designed to unify task management. By automatically ingesting tasks from multiple communication channels, Niyro acts as your centralized intelligence layer.</p>
        <p>Instead of manually tracking what's due, you let Niyro handle the extraction, organization, and reminders. When it's time to work, Niyro's dedicated Focus Mode blocks out the noise so you can execute.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="brutalist-card">
        <h2>How Ingestion Works (User Flow)</h2>
        <p>The cornerstone of Niyro is its seamless task ingestion. We designed it to be completely frictionless, removing the need for manual data entry.</p>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Connect & Forget:</strong> You connect your Google account securely via OAuth in the Niyro dashboard.</li>
            <li><strong>The "Niyro" Label:</strong> Once connected, Niyro automatically generates a special label named <code>Niyro</code> in your Gmail inbox.</li>
            <li><strong>Intentional Tagging:</strong> When you receive an email containing actionable items (e.g., a project brief from a client), you simply apply the <code>Niyro</code> label to it. You don't have to leave Gmail.</li>
            <li><strong>Autonomous Polling:</strong> Every 15 minutes, a Cloud Scheduler cron job quietly polls your inbox for any emails containing the <code>Niyro</code> label.</li>
            <li><strong>AI Extraction:</strong> Niyro extracts the raw text and sends it to our custom Ingestion Agent powered by Gemini. The agent intelligently reads the context, extracts the core task, estimates how long it will take, identifies any hard deadlines, and breaks the task down into smaller actionable steps.</li>
            <li><strong>Task Creation & Cleanup:</strong> The parsed task is instantly pushed to your Niyro dashboard via real-time Firestore listeners. Simultaneously, Niyro removes the <code>Niyro</code> label from the email in your inbox to ensure it is never processed twice.</li>
        </ol>
        <p><em>The exact same flow applies to our Slack and Telegram integrations via real-time push Webhooks!</em></p>
    </div>

    <div class="brutalist-card">
        <h2>The AI Agents of Niyro</h2>
        <p>Niyro is powered by a swarm of specialized AI agents working together asynchronously to manage your workflow.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Ingestion Agent:</strong> Reads messy, unstructured text (from emails or chat messages) and synthesizes it into a highly structured JSON Task object. Triggers automatically via Gmail polling or webhooks.</li>
            <li><strong>Risk Calculation Engine:</strong> Scans your database of pending tasks and compares estimated completion times against hard deadlines. Triggers nightly via Cloud Scheduler to assign visual risk levels (on_track, at_risk, critical).</li>
            <li><strong>Recommendations Agent:</strong> Analyzes historical task completion data, momentum scores, and estimation accuracy to generate personalized advice. Triggers nightly via Cloud Scheduler.</li>
            <li><strong>Executor Agent:</strong> Acts on your behalf to resolve issues (e.g., drafts an email to a client for an extension). Triggers on-demand through explicit commands in the AI Chat.</li>
            <li><strong>RAG Chat Agent:</strong> A conversational interface utilizing Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) over your tasks and database. Acts as your personal chief of staff.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="brutalist-card">
        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Multi-Channel Task Ingestion:</strong> Automatically aggregates tasks and deadlines via Gmail, Telegram, and Slack.</li>
            <li><strong>Conversational AI Assistant:</strong> A context-aware chat interface utilizing Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) over your personal task data.</li>
            <li><strong>Predictive Risk Engine:</strong> Continuously analyzes pending tasks and deadlines, flagging items below critical thresholds.</li>
            <li><strong>Automated Daily Briefings:</strong> Synthesizes the day's priorities into a concise summary delivered every morning.</li>
            <li><strong>Customizable Focus Mode:</strong> A dedicated brutalist environment with visual countdown timers designed to block out distractions.</li>
            <li><strong>AI Recommendations:</strong> Curates personalized coaching advice to iteratively optimize your workflow.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

